Modifications by John (2025-2026):
- Added GPU acceleration support (CUDA, TensorRT, CoreML, DirectML)
- Added --provider, --device-id, --batch-size CLI options
- Implemented adaptive token-budget batching for optimized embedding generation
- Chunks sorted by length to minimize padding waste
- Dynamic batch sizing based on model dimensions
- Environment variable DEMONGREP_TOKEN_BUDGET for tuning

